<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0130001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0130001">本文 Kallakālena 是 Kallakālenaṁ？</note>
<note n="0131002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131002">kharāpiṇḍa 歐魯登貝魯庫英譯為波璃園，應為土塊、岩石等粉狀揑聚硬園之意。</note>
<note n="0131003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131003">象壁（hatthipākāra）浮彫象之姿於上層之壁（天沼俊一著印度遊行記五二一頁參照）。</note>
<note n="0131004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131004">本文 Lañjatisso 是 Lajjitisso？</note>
<note n="0131005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131005">如依此之個所大王統史（三十三．二二）當為三之華供養壇（pupphayāna）tilañcanaṁ 完全不明，暫依用大王統史之文。</note>
<note n="0131006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131006">本文 Kumbhilādhilmanoramaṁ 是 Kumbhilātimanoramaṁ？</note>
<note n="0131007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131007">本文 kam 是 tam？</note>
<note n="0132008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0132008">本文 āntarikā ca bhūpati 是 antarikā camūpatī？</note>
<note n="0132009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0132009">本文 bhikkhu mahāmati 是 bhikkhū mahāmatī？</note>
<note n="0132010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0132010">本文 bhikkhu 是 bhikkhū！</note>
<note n="0132011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0132011">本文 Sivo nāma 是 s ca（or' ti）？</note>
<note n="0133012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0133012">本文 dadatthāya 是 tad（a）atthāya？</note>
<note n="0133013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0133013">依據歐魯登貝魯庫之推定文，即／Khemaṁ ca Duggaṁ khanāpesi（or gaṇhapesi）talākaṁ tāvakālikaṁ／Setuppalāvapiṁ khanāpesi（gaṇhāpesi？）Vaṇṇakaliṁ monoramaṁ＼。</note>
</p>
